00:07:43.750 --> 00:07:46.800
Another request was
hosted in-app purchases.

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:49.880
And in-app purchase, obviously,
is something that you can

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:51.390
use to monetize your games.

00:07:51.400 --> 00:07:52.530
Many of you know this.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:55.900
If you've got freemium,
you're using the freemium model.

00:07:55.900 --> 00:07:58.760
And if you have something that you
sell in your game that involves

00:07:58.850 --> 00:08:01.830
downloading additional content,
Apple can provide for the

00:08:01.830 --> 00:08:05.480
hosting of that content,
up to 2 gigabytes of content.

00:08:05.480 --> 00:08:07.380
We announced this at WDC this past year.

00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:11.140
There's no additional cost involved,
and we simply provide this

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:13.250
hosting service to you.

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:15.470
And so it's super easy to use.

00:08:15.550 --> 00:08:18.340
This was a big request,
and it's now here for

00:08:18.340 --> 00:08:20.080
you to take advantage of.

00:08:20.140 --> 00:08:25.580
And for those of you who have paid apps,
we expanded the volume purchase program.

00:08:25.600 --> 00:08:29.060
And what this really means for you
is this is a way for you to sell

00:08:29.190 --> 00:08:33.460
