00:14:41.750 --> 00:14:44.520
I mean, there are great games
on the platform today,

00:14:44.520 --> 00:14:48.530
but what we want to talk about this
morning is next-generation iOS games.

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:52.810
So first and foremost,
a next-generation game

00:14:52.810 --> 00:14:54.700
needs to be a great game.

00:14:56.000 --> 00:15:00.000
