00:21:21.210 --> 00:21:23.620
And lastly, games,
great games are polished.

00:21:23.620 --> 00:21:26.250
And this is all about
having an attractive design,

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:29.750
which actually ties back to
leaving a great first impression.

00:21:29.750 --> 00:21:32.190
And polished games look gorgeous.

00:21:32.260 --> 00:21:35.430
And they feel just right on iOS.

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:37.080
They're designed for iOS.

