00:21:57.860 --> 00:21:58.770
There should be feedback.

00:21:58.910 --> 00:22:01.400
They don't have to look like
standard UIKit controls,

00:22:01.470 --> 00:22:04.280
they can be completely custom UI,
but if it looks like a button,

00:22:04.320 --> 00:22:06.440
it should behave like a button,
because people on iOS,

00:22:06.440 --> 00:22:10.340
people on these devices expect
all apps to behave certain ways.

00:22:10.340 --> 00:22:14.270
And lists within your game
should scroll and be responsive

00:22:14.270 --> 00:22:16.360
