momentarily to go do something else.

00:22:46.360 --> 00:22:50.170
You want to pause and provide a really
great experience and save the state

00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:53.920
and hold things where they're at,
and then give a good experience

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:59.170
for players coming back into
the game once they return to it.

00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:02.810
And polished games handle
device rotation correctly.

