00:26:41.270 --> 00:26:43.880
horsepower in the palm of your hand.

00:26:43.970 --> 00:26:47.160
And no one else has
done anything like this.

00:26:47.250 --> 00:26:52.990
And the A7 has got a brand-new CPU and a
GPU that provides tons of computational

00:26:52.990 --> 00:26:55.160
power for the most demanding apps.

00:26:55.160 --> 00:27:00.090
And we're just beginning to see
stuff come out now that's taking

00:27:00.090 --> 00:27:03.200
full advantage of this horsepower.

00:27:03.950 --> 00:27:07.160
Now, with 64-bit architecture,
