It's amazing.

00:31:10.560 --> 00:31:13.400
And that's just one example of
what's possible with the new

00:31:13.510 --> 00:31:17.320
64-bit A7 chip that's powering
the iPhone 5s and the new iPads.

00:31:17.380 --> 00:31:22.310
And frankly, if there's nothing else you
take away from today and no

00:31:22.720 --> 00:31:25.860
further guidance that you,
you know, take from Apple,

00:31:25.860 --> 00:31:29.980
it would be that taking advantage
of this horsepower is probably the

00:31:30.130 --> 00:31:34.480
most important thing that you can do
to build a next-generation iOS game.

00:31:35.740 --> 00:31:38.750
If nothing else,
if you just build a great game and

00:31:39.170 --> 00:31:43.600
take advantage of this horsepower,
